sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant MediaServer as Media Server
    participant Storage as Storage System
    participant Monitoring as Monitoring System

    User->>MediaServer: Upload media file
    MediaServer->>Storage: Store media file
    Storage-->>MediaServer: Confirm storage success
    MediaServer-->>User: Confirm upload completion

    Monitoring->>MediaServer: Check upload throughput
    MediaServer-->>Monitoring: Provide throughput metrics
    Monitoring->>User: Report upload status and completion time